$$DM=\sqrt{AD^2-AM^2}=\sqrt{(2s)^2-\left(\frac{2s\sqrt{2}}{3}\right)^2}=\frac{2s\sqrt{3}}{3}.$$

Therefore, $\tan\angle DMB = DM/MB = 2\sqrt{3}/3$. Substituting into the formula above, we get:

$$\tan\angle AMB = \frac{0+2\sqrt{3}/3}{1-0\cdot2\sqrt{3}/3}=\frac{2\sqrt{3}}{3},$$

